reviewText: My daughter loved these for her birthday
Loved this series when I was younger.  Can't wait to watch it again.

The show on the discs are perfectly fine.
But the state of the case was terrible. Now happy with the state I received it.
But happy with the discs.
It was a gift for Christmas

Several of the episodes won't play. I hate tried in two separate players with the same result. I even tried a DVD player cleaning disc hoping this was the issue but alas, it was to no avail. Sure wish quality control was better these days
I HAVE BEEN LOOKING FOR THESE FOR A LONG TIME. THERE GREAT THANKS
Great delivery time thankyou and excellent product

I really appreciated receiving these episodes to watch again.  The five seasons of Highway to Heaven was excellent & I'm so glad that I was able to get them!  All of the disks were in excellent shape without any problems for them.

I'm so glad that I ordered them from The Zone Shop.  The price was reasonable & so was the shipping.  I'm so thankful that ALL of the episodes
were available to watch!

I feel really badly that both Micheal Landon & Victor French died, because they were both wonderful.

Thank you The Zone Shop & Amazon for offering all 5 seasons.
